long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Chewy Reviews Scraper | Images, auto scrape, extract and download reviews from Chewy product listings, including images, and you can one click to export to xlsx/csv file.

# Features
✓ Download reviews from Chewy product listings, including images
✓  Support Sort by and Filter by
✓ Export as XLSX (Excel Document) and CSV
✓ Sort by Author, Rating, Review Date, Helpful count, etc. on Dashboard

# It's free?
Yes, Chewy Reviews Scraper | Images is free. You can get basic functionality and upgrade to get more functionality.
